139
00:10:56,564 --> 00:10:58,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I have to do something.</i></b></font>

140
00:10:58,034 --> 00:11:01,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Anything I can do, I'll do it!</i></b></font>

