<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I-I've done it now...</i></b></font>

142
00:11:47,054 --> 00:11:50,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Did he miscalculate his speed</i>
<i>when crossing the curbside?</i></b></font>

143
00:11:53,294 --> 00:11:55,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The suspension isn't working!</i></b></font>

144
00:11:55,994 --> 00:11:58,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It's no good...</i></b></font>

145
00:11:58,394 --> 00:11:59,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I lost!</i></b></font>

146
00:12:44,544 --> 00:12:48,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't believe it.
To think you'd lose this way...</b></font>

147
00:12:48,214 --> 00:12:50,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm real sorry.</b></font>

148
00:12:50,044 --> 00:12:54,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Now, I'm not trying to make excuses,
but it got hot all of a sudden, right?</b></font>

149
00:12:54,984 --> 00:13:00,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I lost my appetite, and started thinking,
maybe I'm just tired inside.</b></font>

150
00:13:00,724 --> 00:13:05,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But vomiting while driving...
I still can't believe it myself.</b></font>

151
00:13:05,464 --> 00:13:09,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Too bad you didn't puke
while headin' to the goal line.</b></font>

152
00:13:09,134 --> 00:13:11,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It was just a little farther, y'know.</b></font>

153
00:13:11,334 --> 00:13:14,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That wouldn't have been smart at all.</b></font>

154
00:13:14,034 --> 00:13:17,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>For one thing, I couldn't
maintain concentration.</b></font>

155
00:13:17,144 --> 00:13:21,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The tiredness hit me all at once,
like a hole opening up in a dam.</b></font>

156
00:13:21,514 --> 00:13:23,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You'd been racing for so long...</b></font>

157
00:13:23,684 --> 00:13:26,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I didn't think it would be this drawn out.</b></font>

158
00:13:26,814 --> 00:13:31,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'd expected it to be over one round earlier.</b></font>

159
00:13:31,654 --> 00:13:37,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This means the man they've called
a god is now just a middle-aged guy.</b></font>

160
00:13:39,194 --> 00:13:41,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is a bit of a handful.</b></font>

161
00:13:41,734 --> 00:13:44,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We'll have to run an alignment
check once we're back in Gunma.</b></font>

162
00:13:44,934 --> 00:13:47,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Does it look like it can be driven back?</b></font>

163
00:13:47,074 --> 00:13:50,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It'll be fine so long as it runs at a normal speed.</b></font>

164
00:13:50,274 --> 00:13:52,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm sorry.</b></font>

165
00:13:52,444 --> 00:13:55,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't be so down.
The car will be soon repaired.</b></font>

166
00:13:55,344 --> 00:13:56,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah...</b></font>

167
00:13:56,514 --> 00:14:01,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I was the one who instructed you to use
the curbside, though aware of the risk.</b></font>

168
00:14:01,724 --> 00:14:04,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You may feel you've lost in
terms of driving techniques,</b></font>

169
00:14:04,954 --> 00:14:07,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but the end result is, you won.</b></font>

170
00:14:07,454 --> 00:14:12,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That may be so, but I...</b></font>

171
00:14:12,534 --> 00:14:14,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This was a good learning experience.</b></font>

172
00:14:14,604 --> 00:14:17,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The key point this time was the line.</b></font>

173
00:14:17,064 --> 00:14:22,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Your perception of the racing
line has changed, hasn't it?</b></font>

174
00:14:22,074 --> 00:14:27,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't forget this experience today.
You're still learning... developing.</b></font>

175
00:14:27,914 --> 00:14:30,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Both you and Project D.</b></font>

176
00:14:30,914 --> 00:14:34,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Now get some rest. With the
Eight-Six in this condition,</b></font>

177
00:14:34,784 --> 00:14:38,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>the timed race will consist solely
of Keisuke on the hillclimb.</b></font>

178
00:14:38,124 --> 00:14:39,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>All right.</b></font>

179
00:14:42,064 --> 00:14:45,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Please, Keisuke. Set this course a new record!</b></font>

180
00:14:45,794 --> 00:14:47,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

181
00:14:49,904 --> 00:14:53,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Still, Fujiwara's luck at winning is such</i></b></font>

182
00:14:53,774 --> 00:14:58,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>that it cannot be explained through</i>
<i>mathematical probability theory.</i></b></font>

183
00:14:58,514 --> 00:15:04,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>When racing professional racer</i>
<i>Tomoyuki Tachi, and then tonight...</i></b></font>

184
00:15:04,284 --> 00:15:09,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...he achieved miraculous victories.</i>
<i>He is a mysterious fellow.</i></b></font>

185
00:15:09,284 --> 00:15:13,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Perhaps he was born having been</i>
<i>bestowed with a special something.</i></b></font>

186
00:15:34,814 --> 00:15:36,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You all right?</b></font>

187
00:15:36,784 --> 00:15:39,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah. Somehow or other.</b></font>

188
00:15:39,314 --> 00:15:41,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You'd seem to pretty much
have this in the bag.</b></font>

189
00:15:41,724 --> 00:15:45,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I guess. Unfortunately,
the young'un from Gunma</b></font>

190
00:15:45,354 --> 00:15:48,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>won't be makin' any records
with that car of his.</b></font>

191
00:15:48,494 --> 00:15:50,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The car I used for the timed race,</b></font>

192
00:15:50,664 --> 00:15:54,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I could use that as-is even on the pro circuit.</b></font>

193
00:15:54,234 --> 00:15:57,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Those can't exactly be called
fair conditions, can they?</b></font>

194
00:15:57,204 --> 00:16:01,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If street racing had any regulations,
that'd clearly be against the rules.</b></font>

195
00:16:01,304 --> 00:16:05,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, oh, well. After all, I lost the race...</b></font>

196
00:16:05,714 --> 00:16:09,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I gotta have him let me
save some face in the end!</b></font>

197
00:16:09,584 --> 00:16:12,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What about that downhill kid?</b></font>

198
00:16:12,584 --> 00:16:16,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What if he hadn't busted his Eight-Six
and he could've run the timed race?</b></font>

199
00:16:16,484 --> 00:16:20,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In that case... Hmm...</b></font>

200
00:16:20,894 --> 00:16:23,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I think I could've come through.</b></font>

201
00:16:23,194 --> 00:16:26,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey now, that doesn't sound very confident.</b></font>

202
00:16:26,764 --> 00:16:29,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're saying the course record
that you set with your S2000</b></font>

203
00:16:29,404 --> 00:16:32,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>could be beaten by an Eight-Six?</b></font>

204
00:16:32,274 --> 00:16:34,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't scoff at the idea.</b></font>

205
00:16:34,074 --> 00:16:38,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When it comes to the downhill,
that Eight-Six makes the grade.</b></font>

206
00:16:38,544 --> 00:16:43,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>His speed and concentration were
on a level beyond what I expected.</b></font>

207
00:16:43,544 --> 00:16:48,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just for a second, he got <i>me</i> to
grip the wheel with both hands.</b></font>

208
00:16:53,554 --> 00:16:58,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I get it. He was that good
of an opponent, was he?</b></font>

209
00:16:58,394 --> 00:17:01,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Such perfection at such a young age...</b></font>

210
00:17:01,564 --> 00:17:03,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Frightening, isn't it?</b></font>

211
00:17:14,044 --> 00:17:16,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--How is it?!
--No good.</b></font>

212
00:17:16,084 --> 00:17:21,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Dammit! Even though he set new personal
bests on the second and third tries?!</b></font>

213
00:17:24,624 --> 00:17:26,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No good, huh?</b></font>

214
00:17:31,224 --> 00:17:34,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's give Mr. Toudou a thorough
report on what happened here.</b></font>

215
00:17:34,094 --> 00:17:38,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah. My body feels so
achy that I can't stand it.</b></font>

216
00:17:38,074 --> 00:17:41,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I want to race him again!</b></font>

217
00:17:41,174 --> 00:17:44,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"National Park"</b></font>

218
00:17:41,174 --> 00:17:44,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Touge View Park"</b></font>

219
00:17:48,014 --> 00:17:49,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Too bad, huh?</b></font>

220
00:17:49,684 --> 00:17:51,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It couldn't be helped.</b></font>

221
00:17:51,244 --> 00:17:54,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Still, you ran a good race.</b></font>

222
00:17:54,314 --> 00:17:57,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You mind if I say somethin'?</b></font>

223
00:17:57,154 --> 00:18:00,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're not the kind of driver
who should be here forever.</b></font>

224
00:18:00,924 --> 00:18:05,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you like, I can introduce
you to the right contacts.</b></font>

225
00:18:06,994 --> 00:18:13,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I appreciate the offer, but there are
still things that I have to do here.</b></font>

226
00:18:18,514 --> 00:18:22,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I see. Well, I can't force you.</b></font>

227
00:18:22,384 --> 00:18:23,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>See ya.</b></font>

228
00:18:27,714 --> 00:18:29,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>We're not ready yet.</i></b></font>

229
00:18:31,494 --> 00:18:33,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>There's room to get better and better.</i></b></font>

230
00:18:37,864 --> 00:18:39,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Um...</b></font>

231
00:18:46,704 --> 00:18:53,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let me warn you, though, my style
is irregular and completely my own.</b></font>

232
00:18:53,044 --> 00:18:58,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't know that a driver of your
level will learn anything from it.</b></font>

233
00:18:58,254 --> 00:19:00,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Racing in the God Arm's passenger seat...</b></font>

234
00:19:00,484 --> 00:19:02,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A pretty choice arrangement, no?</b></font>

235
00:19:02,154 --> 00:19:05,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He consented readily and most agreeably.</b></font>

236
00:19:05,824 --> 00:19:09,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Truth be told, I'd like to be
sitting in that seat myself.</b></font>

237
00:19:09,594 --> 00:19:12,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay, shall we go?</b></font>

238
00:19:12,264 --> 00:19:13,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yes, please.</b></font>

239
00:19:17,104 --> 00:19:21,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>For Fujiwara, an experience this
valuable will almost never come along.</b></font>

240
00:19:21,744 --> 00:19:25,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Simply being able to see the techniques
of Toshiya Joshima up close...</b></font>

241
00:19:25,674 --> 00:19:27,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

242
00:19:27,674 --> 00:19:30,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The two of them are a</i>
<i>remarkably similar type of driver.</i></b></font>

243
00:19:30,584 --> 00:19:34,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Fujiwara no doubt made a dramatic impact...</i></b></font>

244
00:19:34,454 --> 00:19:39,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What's incredible about the single-handed</i>
<i>steer isn't racing with one hand.</i></b></font>

245
00:19:39,254 --> 00:19:44,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Keep a close eye out for why that is, Fujiwara.</i></b></font>

246
00:19:49,734 --> 00:19:53,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>D shall continue with its races...</i></b></font>

247
00:19:53,734 --> 00:19:58,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Learn well what you see for</i>
<i>the challenging races to come.</i></b></font>

248
00:19:58,614 --> 00:20:02,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Now, you must simply absorb what you need.</i></b></font>

249
00:20:02,214 --> 00:20:05,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The day will come when it shall be of use.</i></b></font>

250
00:20:13,954 --> 00:20:15,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Not this...
--...situation...</b></font>

251
00:20:15,994 --> 00:20:18,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...friggin' <i>again</i>?</b></font>

252
00:20:22,604 --> 00:20:26,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I swear, you guys' love lives
are dead in the water.</b></font>

253
00:20:26,174 --> 00:20:28,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Come on, Boss, don't say that.</b></font>

254
00:20:28,944 --> 00:20:34,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When I was young, even I always
had a woman or two around.</b></font>

255
00:20:34,944 --> 00:20:39,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Maybe one of us is giving off
a "Women stay back!" aura...</b></font>

256
00:20:39,514 --> 00:20:41,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Could be.</b></font>

257
00:20:42,454 --> 00:20:44,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, why're you looking at me?!</b></font>

258
00:20:47,794 --> 00:20:49,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi!</b></font>

259
00:20:49,964 --> 00:20:51,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They say you won again!</b></font>

260
00:20:51,964 --> 00:20:56,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No... How can I put this? I guess it was a draw.</b></font>

261
00:20:56,304 --> 00:21:00,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just say it already! A win is a win!</b></font>

262
00:21:00,274 --> 00:21:03,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, looking at the big picture,
I can't really say that...</b></font>

263
00:21:03,144 --> 00:21:06,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're in the Impreza today?
Where's the Eight-Six?</b></font>

264
00:21:06,114 --> 00:21:11,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The underbody was damaged in
yesterday's race. It's still being fixed.</b></font>

265
00:21:11,484 --> 00:21:14,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--So you're free today?!
--Yeah...</b></font>

266
00:21:14,514 --> 00:21:17,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Then what do you say we do
a long overdue run together?</b></font>

267
00:21:17,824 --> 00:21:20,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Right, Iketani? Kenji?</b></font>

268
00:21:20,354 --> 00:21:24,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, that'd be great! Maybe I'll have
Takumi show me a thing or two!</b></font>

269
00:21:24,724 --> 00:21:25,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

270
00:21:25,894 --> 00:21:28,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We're all young and girlfriend-less,
so we should add Takumi to the ranks</b></font>

271
00:21:28,864 --> 00:21:31,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and <i>bam</i>, do it up!</b></font>

272
00:21:33,674 --> 00:21:36,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Honestly, four fine young men, and yet...</i></b></font>

273
00:21:36,004 --> 00:21:39,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>--...all so sadly lacking when it comes to women.</i>
--By the way, where's Project D going to next?</b></font>

274
00:21:39,574 --> 00:21:44,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't know. But no matter where we
go or who we face, I'll give it my all.</b></font>

275
00:21:44,714 --> 00:21:46,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So <i>cool</i>!</b></font>

276
00:21:46,984 --> 00:21:49,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, not at all...</b></font>

277
00:21:51,694 --> 00:21:53,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}<i>I got no impression</i></b></font>

278
00:21:51,924 --> 00:21:55,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It's for my own sake.</i></b></font>

279
00:21:55,564 --> 00:21:58,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}<i>This town is made by imitation</i></b></font>

280
00:21:55,894 --> 00:22:01,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>There are still so many things I have left to do.</i></b></font>

281
00:21:59,734 --> 00:22:03,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}<i>Wanting your sensation</i></b></font>

282
00:22:03,264 --> 00:22:06,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}<i>In this silly situation</i></b></font>

283
00:22:06,504 --> 00:22:09,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}<i>I wanna rage my dream</i></b></font>

284
00:22:10,404 --> 00:22:14,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Fujiwara Tofu Shop"</b></font>

285
00:22:21,684 --> 00:22:25,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Fujiwara Tofu Shop"</b></font>

286
00:22:28,124 --> 00:22:29,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is she fixed?</b></font>

287
00:22:29,694 --> 00:22:32,034
